1xxx diverse typen, VIP Flights, 32 Sqn
2xxx VC-10, 10 squadron
3xxx Tristar
4xxx C-130 Hercules, Lyneham Transport
Wing
5xxx C-130 Hercules, Lyneham Transport
Wing
